    "abstract": "Aim of this short note is to study Shannon's entropy power along entropic interpolations, thus generalizing Costa's concavity theorem. We shall provide two proofs of independent interest: the former by $\\Gamma$-calculus, hence applicable to more abstract frameworks; the latter with an explicit remainder term, reminiscent of [20], allowing us to characterize the case of equality.",
